  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center in Calhoun County AL?",
  "response": "If you are looking for an inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center in Calhoun County, Alabama, one option to consider is the **Bradford Health Services** facility. Bradford Health Services has a reputation for providing comprehensive addiction treatment and offers various programs tailored to meet individual needs, including inpatient services.\n\nAnother option may be the **RMC Anniston** (Regional Medical Center), which occasionally offers addiction treatment services. It would be helpful to contact them directly to verify current availability and specific programs.\n\nBefore making a decision, consider reaching out to each facility directly to inquire about their specific services, treatment approaches, and to find out if they fit your particular needs. It's also a good idea to consult with a healthcare professional for personalized recommendations.",
